Stop the practice of granting cash advances with no specific purpose or with vaguely described purpose in the Disbursement Voucher (DV) particularly for labor payroll. Henceforth, all cash advances for special purpose shall be clearly described in the disbursement voucher and payroll by indicating the project name, duration, and/or any other material information that would clearly state the specific purpose at a glance;
Direct the accountable officers to fully substantiate with complete supporting attachments both the grant and liquidation of cash advances;
Instruct the Accounting Office to ensure that all transactions of the LGU are well accounted for, recorded, and posted to their respective GLs to ensure accuracy of the financial reports which may affect decision making of the Management; and
