Follow the provisions of COA Circular 2020-006 on the one-time cleansing of PPE account balances and direct the Inventory Committee to complete the inventory taking of all PPE of the Municipal Government, prepare the Inventory Count Form, and upon completion of the physical count, prepare the RPCPPE for submission to the COA Audit Team.

