Zero collections reported for OR Nos. 4892851-4892882 per RCD No. REM-VGR00098 dated December 11, 2023 and cashbook of collecting officer;
Double-reporting of the 18 ORs per e-TRACS-generated RCD dated December 11, 2023 and manually generated RCD dated December 29, 2023;
Delayed remittance of collections for the 16 ORs issued on February 2023 and 2 ORs issued on March 2023 totaling ₱55,278.20;
Alterations on the month of issue on the duplicate copies of ORs;
The Municipal Treasurer enforce the issuance of ORs using the    e-TRACS and stop the manual issuance of ORs to avoid opportunities for delayed remittance of collection and alteration of dates.

We recommended, and the management agreed, that the City Mayor direct the City
Accountant to:
