We recommended that Management: Direct  the  Provincial  Accountant  to ensure the prompt preparation of the Bank Reconciliation Statements and submit them to the Audit Team, together with the corresponding Journal Entry Vouchers (JEVs), paid checks and original copies of Debit and Credit Memos, for review. Also, look into the possibility of using the snapshot of the bank statements as far as practicable under the circumstances to facilitate the preparation of the BRS;

